Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,292)}M.mucedo: 蜂毛霉菌 霉白霉菌\N學名Mucor mucedo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼辦好啊 美里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先冷靜下來 好好想辦法
