Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,17)}C.tricoides：黑霉\N學名Cladosporium tricoides
