Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,17)}Geotrichum sp.：地霉屬\N全稱不明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an9\pos(854,192)}A.niger：黑曲霉\N學名Aspergillus niger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少募集來的錢也得想法兒還掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把房間裡有的東西拿去賣掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們二位是打算用那個酒做買賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃在春季學院祭典上開店的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是拜託我們就能便宜搞到酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從開店的那幫傢伙手裡收集了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是用集資的錢造的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情進展的順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積壓的宿舍費也能還清了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下 正好想和澤木你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 能先通一下風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霉的數量超過玩笑的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 澤木 你能看到菌對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能用那個能力設法賺點錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}比如說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間裡有沒有新種類的菌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 不是新種類也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸菌之類的 能夠賣上價錢的啥玩意兒有不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27\fad(0,100)}松茸菌：學名Tricholoma matsutake
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們招待到這裡 原來是這樣的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過遺憾的是 在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淨是黑霉 青霉之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青霉菌嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青霉菌是從青霉之一 chrysogenum製成的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤木你能夠分辨菌對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼也能純粹的培養吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉一個這傢伙 丟進培養皿就可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,17)}P.chrysogenum\N學名Penicillium chrysogenum\N所謂的青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是看不到啦 不過大體就是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純粹的P.chrysogenum的菌株的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能賣到實驗室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺去和培養科交涉看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤木的能力要掩蓋好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點要主張能夠製造百分百純淨的這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這麼說來我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一直收集青霉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就當作相識也是某種緣分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會給你賺頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺頭是指…錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「青霉這種東西 我家多得是能賣」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺被培養的教授給說了
 Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我開窗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 川濱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你養的大鍬賣掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27\fad(0,100)}大鍬：學名Dorcus hopei 一種珍貴甲蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們是我的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒招兒啊 不想辦法不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你把我給你的蠶「蚕」的幼蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠶「蚕」絲剝下來拿去賣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}木盒上的字：蠶 「蚕」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是你給我的蠶「蚕」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果只是蛾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都死光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要咋辦啊 丫的 你倒是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦 知道了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冬蟲夏草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬蟲夏草？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說中國的那個長生不老的秘藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都死了被腐敗菌吞噬著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,312)}腐敗菌：能夠腐敗有機物的菌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs20\bord2\shad0\3c&Hc080ff&}{\fad(100,100)}{\an7\pos(18,104)}C.sinensis：冬蟲夏草菌\N學名Cordyceps sinensis
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有一隻被冬蟲夏草菌包圍著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來倒是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你是怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 記得大橋那裡的關口阿姨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人經常郵購這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級小的盒子 好像說是2萬塊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2萬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}囧 當然是日元啦 大概RMB1300
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然的因為很難找到 貌似很貴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個培養下 不能賣到中藥店什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤木 拜託啦 幫俺們一把
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是可以啦 這點小事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬蟲夏草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}真的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能解決了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要慶祝慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤木 這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 從來沒有人因為我能看到菌這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}萬歲 萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人依賴 還真是件愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}萬歲 萬歲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}囧 這倆人胳膊不酸麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤木君的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了他們倆的手上 也不過是賺錢的工具麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣我也有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,351)\fs20\fr17\fad(200,0)}{\bord0\shad0\1c&H000000&}估\N價\N單\N在\N內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生要賠償這個金額的話應該很困難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27}為了歡迎你倆入學 為了我們的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(443,167)}{\fs20\bord0\shad0\1c&H000000&}{\fad(0,1000)}蠶「蚕」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長谷川同學今天已經要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我還有想要做的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs27}告知：\N\N{\fs20}以下的人請於本日10點 到舊農學部西棟樹研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}一年 澤木直保 結城螢\N二年川濱拓馬 美里熏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}不來你們就慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 不過明天你要空出時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已經漆黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去樹老師那裡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書包落在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正大家都還在睡 趁現在去了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有像長谷川小姊和樹老師那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要考驗我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常的話要麼躲遠要麼懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會覺得不快的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 澤木君他好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏說看到了 真是噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤木家的直保 真是有點與眾不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:18:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說很多怪話企圖引起注意 也是小孩子常做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼能看到菌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不想吃 就直接說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說謊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 直保  快吃飯打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 直保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住 要飛了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這幫傢伙久違地玩玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠色的 到這邊集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃色的霉就把飯團當作托盤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 這不是澤木的另一半嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你還在學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在剛才惹事的那兩個學長的宿舍裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 書包忘在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這事啊 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很辛苦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後 你打算怎樣和澤木相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎樣…我們之間沒有任何問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況是酒廠和種麴店的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計會成為畢生之交…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來給你個善意的忠告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子能看到菌的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我們的一套透射電子顯微鏡相當 這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有3億元的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs27\fad(0,100)}3億日元 大概人民幣2000萬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3億元麼…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子的能力被人知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖利用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不會僅僅是樹老師和鬍子和胖子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菌劇場 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.80,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫chrysogenum 俗稱青霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(110,100)}{\1c&H9EA35B&}chrysogenum
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(110,416)}{\1c&H9EA35B&}青 霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡濕氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是tricoides
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\1c&HA68891&}{\pos(110,70)}tricoides
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在浴室的地磚縫隙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是變黑的地方啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也被叫做黑霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\1c&HA68891&}{\pos(110,70)}黑 霉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 好啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真是熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,100)}{\1c&Hc67d04&}alternata
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,200)}{\1c&Hc67d04&}鏈格孢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是alternata 俗稱鏈格孢霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好保養的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是隱形眼鏡的洗滌液 也會釀掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空調的內部也隱藏著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是霉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你丫個霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間 到處都是霉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個棒房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:29.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(178,135)\fs30}菌劇第3話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:29.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(579,375)\fs30}由我們來釀造
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 大家知道醃魟魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:34.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(681,402)\fs28}用菌醃製哦!


